Package space.sunqian.common.object.data

Interface MapSchema

All Superinterfaces:
DataSchema
@Immutable public interface MapSchema extends DataSchema
This interface represents the schema of map, provides information about the map's entries.

Two MapSchemas are considered equal if, and only if both types of maps and both parsers from parser() are equal.
